message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper proposes a fully automatic method for segmentation and disease classification using cardiac cine MR images, which involves the use of convolutional neural networks (CNN) for segmentation and Random Forest classifier for disease classification. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with medical imaging (cs.MED) and the use of neural networks (cs.NEURON) for medical diagnosis.
